# Release Notes - v2.4.2 (2026-04-15 02:30 UTC)

- 🛡️ **Rock-Solid Data**: Enhanced database stability ensures your information is always safe and accessible.
- 🌳 **Structured Success**: Manage complex projects effortlessly with new hierarchical tasks and subtask support.
- 🧠 **AI-Powered Agility**: Let our intelligent engine handle task transitions in the background while you focus on what matters.
- 📊 **Effortless Reporting**: Generate deep insights without the wait using our new asynchronous reporting system.

